2 Issues Identified
 Slang Words
brooo → bro
luv → love
plz → please
gr8 → great
w8 → wait
btw → by the way

Emojis
😎 😂 ❤️ 🎉 😍 😴 😋 😒 🎊
These convey emotion/sentiment
Typos / Informal Text
Gud → Good
mrng → morning
amazng → amazing
knw → know
hpy → happy
goin → going

3 Preprocessing Steps Needed
 1 Lowercasing

 Convert all text to lowercase
 “Hello” → “hello”

 2 Remove Special Characters

 Remove symbols like !!!, @, ?
 “Hello!!!” → “hello”

 3 Handle Emojis
 Remove OR Convert to meaning (😊 → happy)

 4 Expand Slang / Short Forms
 “plz” → “please”
 “gr8” → “great”

 5 Correct Typos
 Use spell correction
 “amazng” → “amazing”

 6 Remove Extra Letters
  “soooo” → “so”

 7 Tokenization
 Split sentence into words
 “I love AI” → [I, love, AI]

 8 Stopword Removal (Optional)
 Remove words like “is”, “the”, “a”
 Example (Before → After)

 Before:
 "I luv this movie sooo much ❤️"

 After Cleaning:
 "i love this movie so much"

